  "about": {
    "heading": "About Highlight",
    "paragraphs": [
      "Highlight Coffee is Glendale's destination for specialty coffee. We source single-origin beans from world-class roasters and brew every cup with meticulous care — whether it's a perfectly extracted espresso or a slow-drip pour-over.",
      "Our bright, modern space on East Broadway is built for coffee lovers who appreciate quality. Come for the coffee, stay for the atmosphere. With a 4.6-star rating and nearly 300 five-star reviews, we've become a staple in the Glendale coffee scene."
    ]
